# 2004 Prince Edward Island Scott Tournament of Hearts

The 2004 Prince Edward Island Scott Tournament of Hearts was held on Jan. 22â€“27 at the Cornwall Curling Club in Cornwall, Prince Edward Island. The winning team was Team Suzanne Gaudet, who represented Prince Edward Island, and they finished with a 2-9 round-robin record at the 2004 Scott Tournament of Hearts in Red Deer, Alberta.
